strings.Value: "You know what I like about you? You're almost the only one here who's not trying to tell me that I live the wrong way!"
"Oh, live however you like, what do I care? Each of us writes their own story."
"And you know why? I don't see any point in wasting my time on an arrogant bully who never listens to anyone anyway."
